@startuml
title SomeTrails Password Reset
actor User
participant "Login Form"    as LF
participant "Auth Server"   as AS
participant "User Database" as DB
participant "Email Service" as ES

User -> LF  : Click "Forgot password"
LF   -> User : Prompt for email
User -> LF  : Enter email
LF   -> AS  : Request reset
AS   -> DB  : Lookup email
DB   --> AS : User found
AS   -> ES  : Send reset email with token
ES   --> User : Deliver reset link
User -> AS  : Open link, submit new password
AS   -> DB  : Update password hash
DB   --> AS : Updated
AS   --> User : Confirm reset complete

@enduml
